text: Elyorjon Mamadaliev (born 5 February 1995) is an Uzbekistani sprint canoeist.Profile He won a medal at the 2019 ICF Canoe Sprint World Championships.2019 ICF Canoe Sprint World Championships results ==References== Category:1995 births Category:Living people Category:ICF Canoe Sprint World Championships medalists in Canadian Category:Uzbekistani male canoeists Category:Asian Games medalists in canoeing Category:Canoeists at the 2018 Asian Games Category:Asian Games silver medalists for Uzbekistan Category:Medalists at the 2018 Asian Games
